# BEGIN ###########################
insert usb installer into machine

first step is to drop machine to BIOS
each motherboard has own hot-key range F2-F12

power on
BIOS banner tells proper hotkey fast

find the hot-key F2-F12
this will drop to BIOS 

you may need to reboot many times
# BIOS step two ###################
Be curious in BIOS
Write down cpu processor architecture
discover if computer supports amd64

look for boot options
installer-usb must boot first

save & exit BIOS
FreeBSD demon will display if correct
# comment #########################
the first portion 'data=...' takes substantial time
ssd will read it fast; hdd a bit slow;
usb if so slow you can read 'data=...'
# good luck #######################
curiousity & relentlessness rewards answer
trial & error is the action of the hacker
